Thank you for applying for a Rare Pride campaign. We appreciate you taking the time to help us
get to know your organization better.   
<br/>
<br/>Submitting this form is required and is the first step in the application process for the Rare 
Pride Program but does not commit you or your organization to any further action. Once you submit this 
form, you will receive an email alerting you that we have received your information. We will contact 
you two weeks after you receive the email by email or phone to discuss next steps. If you have not heard 
from us within two weeks, or have additional questions, please contact Khanh Nguyen, Partnership Manager 
at knguyen@rareconservation.org.
 
<br/>
</p>
